1990
00:52:16,800 --> 00:52:19,719
[SPEAKER_00] I koji dio smiješ pipkati.

1991
00:52:19,719 --> 00:52:20,719
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne moraš da ispojiti.

1992
00:52:20,719 --> 00:52:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ok.

1993
