[SPEAKER_00] Crkva je majka.

1996
00:52:26,360 --> 00:52:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ali si spomenio malo prije.

1997
00:52:30,559 --> 00:52:32,179
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže,

1998
00:52:32,179 --> 00:52:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] kad me pitaju ljude,

1999
00:52:34,079 --> 00:52:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] dokle smijem ići,

2000
00:52:35,059 --> 00:52:37,320
[SPEAKER_00] ja bih rekao da je to krivo postavljeno pitanje.

2001
00:52:37,320 --> 00:52:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] Nego,

2002
00:52:38,440 --> 00:52:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je rekao,

2003
00:52:40,380 --> 00:52:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] Isus u Mateje Evanđelije kaže,

2004
00:52:41,980 --> 00:52:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] čuli ste ga rečeno ne činite preljub.

2005
00:52:44,139 --> 00:52:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] A preljub je bilo je konkretan čin.

2006
00:52:45,659 --> 00:52:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže,

2007
