2010
00:52:54,079 --> 00:52:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, sada.

2011
00:52:54,980 --> 00:52:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan od citata,

2012
00:52:56,699 --> 00:52:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] koje Ivan Pavol II citirao u svojim katehezama.

2013
00:52:58,920 --> 00:53:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne znam,

2014
