[SPEAKER_00] vi koji sad slušate ovo,

2015
00:53:01,559 --> 00:53:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] gledate,

2016
00:53:02,039 --> 00:53:02,659
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam,

2017
00:53:02,659 --> 00:53:04,380
