[SPEAKER_00] ali ja bi okrenio ovako,

2022
00:53:09,960 --> 00:53:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] da to treba izazivati u svima nama jedna mogućnost.

2023
00:53:15,440 --> 00:53:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi postavio kontrapitanje Isusu,

2024
00:53:17,760 --> 00:53:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] čeka Isuse,

2025
