[SPEAKER_00] kad mi dođu 16-godišnjaci

2044
00:54:07,420 --> 00:54:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] koji stvarno traže neke odgovore,

2045
00:54:09,679 --> 00:54:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] ok, nemoj započeti neku radnju

2046
00:54:12,380 --> 00:54:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja zapravo će i zazvati u tebi

2047
00:54:16,539 --> 00:54:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] to i uzbuđenje i požudu.

2048
00:54:18,980 --> 00:54:20,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

2049
00:54:20,980 --> 00:54:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] I onda šta ćemo shvatiti jako brzo?

2050
00:54:23,559 --> 00:54:25,280
[SPEAKER_00] To počne u srcu.

2051
00:54:25,280 --> 00:54:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ono Pavlovo, da se svi ne žele ženiti.

2052
00:54:28,679 --> 00:54:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ovako, ja ću ovako krenuti.

2053
00:54:31,159 --> 00:54:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, bračni parovi koji mi služaju,

2054
00:54:33,059 --> 00:54:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] zamisli situaciju da muž dođe jedan dan ženi

2055
00:54:36,139 --> 00:54:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže, ženo, ja te volim

2056
00:54:37,980 --> 00:54:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] i ne želim te prevrti.

2057
00:54:39,300 --> 00:54:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jel možeš ti meni staviti na papiru?

2058
00:54:40,920 --> 00:54:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ima jedna zgodna tajnica kod mene,

2059
00:54:42,719 --> 00:54:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] nabacuje se i ne želim te prevrti.

2060
00:54:44,420 --> 00:54:47,239
[SPEAKER_00] Jel možeš ti meni zapisati

2061
00:54:47,239 --> 00:54:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] dok le ja smijem s njom ići da tebe ne prevrni?

2062
00:54:49,539 --> 00:54:50,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš šta bi ona rekla?

2063
00:54:50,320 --> 00:54:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ne smijuš razmišljati o njoj.

2064
00:54:52,340 --> 00:54:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] Zamisli da muž pita ženu.

2065
00:54:55,599 --> 00:54:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je firma.

2066
00:54:56,500 --> 00:54:58,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, zamisli da muž pita ženu.

2067
00:54:58,780 --> 00:55:01,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ženo, da ti meni reci da me ulakšaš na poslu.

2068
00:55:01,300 --> 00:55:02,659
[SPEAKER_00] imam neku tajnicu tamo.

2069
00:55:02,659 --> 00:55:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] Što smijem s njom raditi, šta ne smijem?

2070
00:55:05,380 --> 00:55:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću te služiti.

2071
00:55:06,019 --> 00:55:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš šta bi ona rekla?

2072
00:55:07,420 --> 00:55:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Daj otkaz na posao.

2073
00:55:09,079 --> 00:55:11,880
[SPEAKER_00] U smislu, ne smijuš je gledat.

2074
00:55:11,880 --> 00:55:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] Jer njegovo srce pripada ženi.

2075
00:55:17,239 --> 00:55:18,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ok?

2076
00:55:18,320 --> 00:55:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] I on ne smije čak srcem je prevariti.

2077
00:55:22,599 --> 00:55:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] I pogledom.

2078
00:55:24,000 --> 00:55:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] A nije pitanje kaj...

2079
00:55:25,239 --> 00:55:27,320
[SPEAKER_00] I zato kad mi mladi pitaju,

2080
00:55:27,320 --> 00:55:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] ja kažem prijatelju,

2081
00:55:30,159 --> 00:55:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] možda će to biti tvoja buduća žena.

2082
00:55:31,619 --> 00:55:32,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to ne znam.

2083
00:55:32,360 --> 00:55:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ali aj budi vjeran tvojoj budućoj ženi.

2084
00:55:34,880 --> 00:55:39,300
[SPEAKER_00] I zato nemoj si dopustiti situaciju

2085
00:55:39,300 --> 00:55:42,360
[SPEAKER_00] gdje pokreneš neku radnju,

2086
00:55:42,360 --> 00:55:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] a već si negdje kao kršćanin katolik odlučio,

2087
00:55:46,940 --> 00:55:48,719
[SPEAKER_00] nećeš s njom spaviti prije braka.

2088
00:55:48,719 --> 00:55:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoj započeti taj proces onda.

2089
00:55:50,079 --> 00:55:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi katolici mi dođu, mladi studenti,

2090
00:55:53,000 --> 00:55:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo odlučili živiti čistoču u braku,

2091
00:55:55,139 --> 00:55:56,099
[SPEAKER_00] nećemo spaviti prije braka.

2092
00:55:56,099 --> 00:55:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] Odlično, čestitam ti.

2093
00:55:57,239 --> 00:55:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, šta smijemo raditi?

2094
00:55:59,699 --> 00:56:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem imanta, dobro,

2095
00:56:00,960 --> 00:56:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] slušaj prijatelju.

2096
00:56:01,900 --> 00:56:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, znaš šta?

2097
00:56:02,820 --> 00:56:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] Boga molim.

2098
00:56:03,340 --> 00:56:05,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, nećeš spavati s njom.

2099
00:56:05,360 --> 00:56:05,820
[SPEAKER_00] Super.

2100
00:56:05,820 --> 00:56:08,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, kad počne taj čin spavanje?

2101
00:56:08,780 --> 00:56:11,179
[SPEAKER_00] Kad počne seks, konkretno?

2102
00:56:11,179 --> 00:56:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] Pitaš nju ili njega?

2103
00:56:13,400 --> 00:56:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, nji dvoje.

2104
00:56:14,500 --> 00:56:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] I dođemo do situacije da počne u srcu.

2105
00:56:19,019 --> 00:56:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] Glupo mi je sad navesti neku predigru.

2106
00:56:21,579 --> 00:56:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kao ono, smiješ ovo, smiješ.

2107
00:56:23,599 --> 00:56:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] To je banalno.

2108
00:56:24,760 --> 00:56:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] E, sada, je li to znači da ću oni...

2109
00:56:28,480 --> 00:56:29,860
[SPEAKER_00] Držati za ruke.

2110
00:56:29,860 --> 00:56:30,980
[SPEAKER_00] Držati za ruke, ok.

2111
00:56:30,980 --> 00:56:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to znači da će biti nježnost?

2112
00:56:32,880 --> 00:56:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] Da, bit će nježnost.

2113
00:56:35,099 --> 00:56:37,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je čari hodanja

2114
00:56:37,440 --> 00:56:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] gdje oni moraju naći svoj modus vivendi

2115
00:56:41,420 --> 00:56:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] gdje oni ću znati,

2116
00:56:43,980 --> 00:56:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] djevoji koji će znati,

2117
00:56:44,920 --> 00:56:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] ok, ja cijenim ovu čistoću,

2118
00:56:47,199 --> 00:56:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] želim je živiti od braka.

2119
00:56:48,280 --> 00:56:50,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam da ovo možda uzbuđuje momka

2120
00:56:50,820 --> 00:56:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo neću raditi jer znam da ovo njega uzbuđuje.

2121
00:56:53,579 --> 00:56:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni čuvaju jedne druge, jel?

2122
00:56:55,980 --> 00:56:58,780
